{"tid":2385702,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"2人藏雷射筆被控管有攻擊性武器罪成 一人判囚5個月一人判入更生中心","createTime":"2021-01-29T07:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T14:30:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e17481b8c2f4501083a649c681cf92018b5dd369","tid":2385702,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:40:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13322\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13322&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=71fd4c88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13322</a><br />\n<br />\n#屯門裁判法院第六庭<br />\n#王證瑜裁判官 <br />\n#1111屯門 #判刑<br />\n<br />\n第一被告：李 （早前已罪名不成立）<br />\n第二被告：譚<br />\n第三被告：甄<br />\n<br />\n控罪：2項管有攻擊性武器<br />\n<br />\n案情：三名被告人被控於2019年11月11日於屯門青賢街成發汽車有限公司的露天停車場，未經許可或批准管有攻擊性武器（鐳射筆)，違反香港法例243章公安條例33條第1，2，3項<br />\n<br />\n2021年1月12日於王證瑜裁判官席前宣讀之簡單裁決理由 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12844&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=413797e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12844</a>)<br />\n========<br />\n第二被告：<br />\n已經收到背景報告，律師已解釋予被告人知及同意。<br />\n呈上七封求情信（被告，媽媽，上司，舊同事，朋友，小學班主任，認識了十多年的朋友）<br />\n求情信顯示被告由細到大均樂於助人，能為公司帶來歡樂，已真心悔過，在案件發生後，有明顯轉變（收工後都會盡快番屋企，避免參與公眾活動），雖然成續平平，但品格優良，富有正義感<br />\n<br />\n（求情信指被告曾抱著友人的小童說道「我一定會為你守衛公義，給你自由嘅香港，一個充滿希望嘅未來」）<br />\n<br />\n第三被告：<br />\n已索取勞教中心及更生中心報告。希望採納報告內容（適合更生中心報告）<br />\n呈上數封求情信（被告，2名姐姐，教會牧師，中學校長等）<br />\n被告沒有刑事定罪記錄，21歲以下，案情非特別嚴重，案發被截停後相對合作，案件中鐳射筆搜獲時為拆開，沒有證據曾使用。<br />\n<br />\n判刑<br />\n法庭指出控罪是嚴重的，法例要求必然是監禁式刑罰。然，法庭接納2位被告背景良好，有家人朋友支持。<br />\n<br />\n第二被告：❗️監禁5個月❗️<br />\n（監禁6個月為量刑起點，考慮求情因素，酌情扣一個月）<br />\n<br />\n第三被告：判入更生中心❗️<br />\n<br />\n直播員按：我地會堅持落去，守衛公義，給下一代自由，充滿希望嘅香港，無論付出什麼代價"},{"pid":"c6d1669c6cd42b01a5271f87fb1b846c103faa21","tid":2385702,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:41:03.000Z","msg":"2名青年前年11月屯門示威期間遭警方追截至停車場後，各被搜出雷射筆，分別被裁定1項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪成。辯方今午在屯門裁判法院求情指27歲售貨員譚俊賢一直奉公守法，犯案屬無心之失，多名師友同事證其品格良好，熱心助人；再求情指20歲男生關心家人，擔保期間持續進修，牧師指其於教會服務克盡己任。裁判官王證瑜最終就前者判囚5個月，後者判入更生中心。"},{"pid":"27648bd9244ca5ac281c344f62834c70bd680df3","tid":2385702,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f7e84cf1fe0db22fbb5af1f881482f7781b946","tid":2385702,"uid":30113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:51:21.000Z","msg":"幾時開始一支咁的筆變左武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b390f25c5d863cb41700954a1835ac6fb5b3e471","tid":2385702,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bae119ad8c369d38b400a566efe29726c08c667","tid":2385702,"uid":70489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:07:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d933d35f5e65f2b3d48089f0ddfd59917a0db1c7","tid":2385702,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:15:08.000Z","msg":"<del></del>"},{"pid":"6c444754bcc63167dc6d861b0a3f74ae2fed44d0","tid":2385702,"uid":39503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雷射筆都告得入？"},{"pid":"3f04423fa57637b48f341d4b08ad84cdd797b341","tid":2385702,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca3747879692253135f2687a132aeb18dd74c85","tid":2385702,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:21:41.000Z","msg":"王官判刑時指，兩名被告的背景良好，獲親友等人支持。<span class=\"red\">由於律政司以《公安條例》起訴，除監禁或禁閉式刑罰外，法庭沒其他判刑選擇</span>。甄姓被告只有19歲，判入更生中心是唯一判刑選項。至於譚姓被告，王官以6個月為量刑起點，念及上述求情因素，酌情扣減1個月，最終判他入獄5個月。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210129/Q4D2HJPEWNHKRBAFOTV2LYP77M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210129%2FQ4D2HJPEWNHKRBAFOTV2LYP77M%2F&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=6078b3f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210129%2FQ4D2HJPEWNHKRBAFOTV2LYP77M%2F&h=dbfa7d95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210129/Q4D2HJPEWNHKRBAFOTV2LYP77M/</a>"},{"pid":"450d1a18ec03271939f61462dd1029b8c4972260","tid":2385702,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T11:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6c8d893968b326bf21858d6a3eee712a4e7480","tid":2385702,"uid":172556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T11:28:50.000Z","msg":"藍屍用刀斬人坐三個月，後生仔拎支筆坐五個月"},{"pid":"bae9149c9488c7e2c08a56a0068a497a150cfc62","tid":2385702,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"支蝗拎刀兇人就無事，香港人袋支 pointer 就坐幾個月。仆街紅官死全家"},{"pid":"d63bc67e6da7d169eed4ec8f343a1502c9e58d94","tid":2385702,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00b866fd1ba287accf3c8a5aba1871e0c6ee213","tid":2385702,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5f7e84cf1fe0db22fbb5af1f881482f7781b946","tid":2385702,"uid":30113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:51:21.000Z","msg":"幾時開始一支咁的筆變左武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:01:24.000Z","msg":"只要你有攻擊人嘅意圖<br />\n你碌鳩都可以係攻擊性武器"},{"pid":"f4c7cb2d401ce7344454d6ba53d2d3aa5338bfcc","tid":2385702,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86e3db985a2bdb2283bce676925d16431e671571","tid":2385702,"uid":185424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:30:21.000Z","msg":"每日見到呢d新聞...真係好痛心<br />\n手足要撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}